tourBios.curYearHigh: Earned exempt status at the PGA TOUR Canada's Florida Qualifying Tournament...In first PGA TOUR Canada start at the season-opening PC Financial Open, finished T7, thanks to weekend rounds of 69-67.

tourBios.curYrHigh: Earned exempt status at the PGA TOUR Canada's Florida Qualifying Tournament...In first PGA TOUR Canada start at the season-opening PC Financial Open, finished T7, thanks to weekend rounds of 69-67.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Two-time All-Sun Belt Conference and an Academic All-American...Captured the 2011 David Toms Intercollegiate.
tourBios.personal: Big New Orleans Saints fan and lists Drew Brees and Tiger Woods as his favorite athletes...Says making the cut in the 2013 Chitimacha Louisiana Open on the Web.com Tour is his biggest thrill in golf...Favorite course is Old Waverly GC...Favorite professional team is the New Orleans Saints.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T7th in 2014 at the PC Financial Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T84th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the PGA TOUR Canada.
